This repository is a replication and study of FedDMC, prepared for a master's
thesis at the University of Namur (2026).

Base code
---------
It is derived from the original FedDMC implementation by Xutong Mu et al.:

    https://github.com/MuXutong/FedDMC

which accompanies the paper:

    Xutong Mu, Ke Cheng, Yulong Shen, Xiaoxiao Li, Zhao Chang, Tao Zhang,
    and Xindi Ma. "FedDMC: Efficient and Robust Federated Learning via
    Detecting Malicious Clients." IEEE Transactions on Dependable and Secure
    Computing, 2024.
    https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/10458320
    DOI: 10.1109/TDSC.2024.3372634

At the time this repository was forked, the original repository carried no
license file. Under default copyright law that makes the original code "all
rights reserved" by its authors. It is included here only for academic
replication, with attribution. Anyone wishing to reuse the original portions
should clear that with the original authors.

Modifications
-------------
The MIT license in LICENSE applies to the modifications and additions made in
this replication, not to the original FedDMC code. The exact changes are
recorded in this repository's git history relative to the upstream fork point.
